gameData

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameData.Field

  • public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    The Field class stores the status of the base paths at any given time in a game of MLB Showdown. Additionally, Field updates the status of the basepaths given a card result and returns GameStat tracking information based on these results. Ideally in the future, it will also process strategy cards, and basically be the main engine of strategy on the field.
    Version:
    .1
    Author:
    Matthew Bunge
